Package: fxconvert
Title: Simple and Tidy Currency Conversion
Version: 0.2.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Magnus Thor", "Torfason", , "m@zulutime.net", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Convert currencies based on rates obtained directly from central
    banks in an open and transparent way, without any API dependencies or 
    registration requirements. Conversion with `fx_convert()` is
    fully vectorized in amounts, currencies, and dates, uses local data when 
    available, and downloads up-to-date rates from a GitHub repository in 
    `parquet` format when needed.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
